  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/CoreText\/CTTextAlignment\/kCTNaturalTextAlignment\ncrawled: 2025-12-14T02:52:36Z\n---\n\n# kCTNaturalTextAlignment\n\n**Type Property**\n\nText uses the natural alignment of the text’s script.\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\nstatic var kCTNaturalTextAlignment: CTTextAlignment { get }\n```\n\n## Deprecated\n\n- **kCTLeftTextAlignment**: Text is visually left-aligned.\n- **kCTRightTextAlignment**: Text is visually right-aligned.\n- **kCTCenterTextAlignment**: Text is visually center-aligned.\n- **kCTJustifiedTextAlignment**: Text is fully justified.\n\n",
